    lemma lemmaGetStateSuchThatInductiveInvariantsForConsistencyAreSatisfiedAndItIsInstrDSStateMultisetSetMessagesSentEquivalentToDestinationInstrDSStateOfHonestMultipleStepHelper<T(!new)>(
